'''Finn Aabye''' (born 7 July 1935, [[Hellerup]]) is a Danish film producer. He was the former director of Danish Film Institute.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/kultur/film/filmfolk-fralaegger-sig-ansvaret-overgreb-paa-mindreaarige-skuespillere|title=Filmfolk fralægger sig ansvaret for overgreb på mindreårige skuespillere|work=DR|access-date=2018-07-25|language=da}}</ref>

